            id="introduction"
          >
            Introduction
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm md:text-base text-[#31393C]">
            This application provides a seamless integration between Instagram
            and ERPNext, enabling users to effortlessly post content and upload
            stories directly from the ERPNext system. With this integration,
            users can streamline their social media management.
          </p>
